<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
    <title></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="timeslot.scss"/>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Noto+Sans+KR" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="jquery-3.4.1.min.js"></script>

  </head>
      
  <body id="time_body">
      
    <div class="left_nav_bar">
        <%= link_to image_tag("logo_3.png", class: "illustration_nav", id: "logoimg"), '/' %>
        <ul class="left_top_nav">

        <hr>
        <li class="left_top_nav_3"><%= link_to '시간표', users_show_path %></li>
        <hr>
        <li class="left_top_nav_3"><%= link_to '회의록', new_post_path %></li>
        <hr>
        </ul>
        <ul class="left_bottom_nav">
        <hr>
        <li><%= link_to '로그아웃', session_path(current_user), method: 'delete'  %></li>
        <hr>
        <ul>
    </div>
    <div class="main_sentence">
        안 되는 시간을 클릭하여<br><span class="blue">회의 시간</span>을 정해보세요.
    </div>
    
    <div class="Rectangle_bus">
        <div class ="top-bar">
            <table id='busmove'>
                <tbody>
                    <tr class="row">
                        <% for i in (1..20) %>
                            <% if i==@progress %>
                                <td class="one"></td>
                                <% next %>
                            <% else %>
                                <td></td>
                            <% end %>
                        <% end %>
                        <div id="top_flag"><%= image_tag "flag.png"%></div>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>

  
    
    <%= form_for(@user) do |f| %>



      <div class="tablebox">
        <table id="time_table">
          <tbody id="time_tbody">
            <tr>
              <td class="timeTableCellDay"></td>
